{"number":109,"ayahs":[{"numberInSurah":1,"arabic":" قُلْ يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلْكَـٰفِرُونَ","translation":"Say, \"O disbelievers,","transliteration":"Qul ya ayyuha alkafiroon","page":603},{"numberInSurah":2,"arabic":"لَآ أَعْبُدُ مَا تَعْبُدُونَ","translation":"I do not worship what you worship.","transliteration":"La aAAbudu ma taAAbudoon","page":603},{"numberInSurah":3,"arabic":"وَلَآ أَنتُمْ عَـٰبِدُونَ مَآ أَعْبُدُ","translation":"Nor are you worshippers of what I worship.","transliteration":"Wala antum AAabidoona maaAAbud","page":603},{"numberInSurah":4,"arabic":"وَلَآ أَنَا۠ عَابِدٌ مَّا عَبَدتُّمْ","translation":"Nor will I be a worshipper of what you worship.","transliteration":"Wala ana AAabidun maAAabadtum","page":603},{"numberInSurah":5,"arabic":"وَلَآ أَنتُمْ عَـٰبِدُونَ مَآ أَعْبُدُ","translation":"Nor will you be worshippers of what I worship.","transliteration":"Wala antum AAabidoona maaAAbud","page":603},{"numberInSurah":6,"arabic":"لَكُمْ دِينُكُمْ وَلِىَ دِينِ","translation":"For you is your religion, and for me is my religion.\"","transliteration":"Lakum deenukum waliya deen","page":603}]}